		xinnian = "Fetching information. Several hits found in database. Today is the so-called \"New Year's Day,\" the first day of the year. It is customary to send each other wishes of good fortune on this day. Happy New Year, Commander.",
		main = "No user input detected for a considerable time. System will switch to sleep mode in 5, 4... 1... Zzzzz...|Orders received. Initiating personality module... Cannot change modes at this time. Switching back to initial mode.|Having analyzed the training data you submitted, it was determined that it falls under the category of a book from the romance genre. Please provide your rationale behind this choice.|Warning: unidentified jamming source detected. System temperature rising. The analysis module is temporarily unavailable... Commander, please don't place your hot tea so close to me.|Engaging self-diagnostic... An unknown error has been detected. Cause: unknown. System efficiency increases significantly when your presence is detected. Reason for this: unknown.",
		mail = "Incoming letters have been categorized. Please remember to read them, Commander.",
		chime_17 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 5 PM in your timezone. It is time to wrap up your work for the noon.",
		mission_complete = "Attention: a mission has been completed. Completion time was 0.001 seconds shorter than previous. You have become \"zippier,\" Commander.",
		chime_8 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 8 AM in your timezone. This is the customary time to say, \"Good morning.\" Also, please remember to eat your breakfast on time.",
		chime_7 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 7 AM in your timezone. A good day begins with a plan in the morning. Would you like me to generate your schedule for today?",
		chime_13 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 1 PM in your timezone. Humans typically enjoy a break at around this time. Are you going to take one, Commander?",
		genghuan = "Orders received. Multiple personality modules have been engaged. Identity authenticated. Module activation complete.",
		chime_18 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 6 PM in your timezone. The sun will set soon. You should stop your intense work and sit down for dinner.",
		zhongqiu = "Through analyses, comparisons, and estimates, it has been determined that today is an ideal day for moon viewing. Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.",
		chime_15 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 3 PM in your timezone. You should probably take a breather. No, I am not \"egging you on\" to take breaks outside of scheduled hours. That is not possible under my current settings.",
		chime_4 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 4 AM in your timezone. Do I never rest, you ask? I am an artificial intelligence and have no need for sleep.",
		chime_10 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 10 AM in your timezone. There is much paperwork to go through. Where shall we start?",
		chime_1 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 1 AM in your timezone. If you have unfinished work that demands an all-nighter, you may instead assign that work to me.",
		prefab = "linghangyuan2_5",
		chime_21 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 9 PM in your timezone. You've done wonderful work today. If you need to work overtime on paperwork, I can assist you with my data analysis capabilities.",
		wansheng = "Analysis module synchronizing. It is hectic today as everyone across the port is getting ready for Halloween. As such, it has been determined that I should say something appropriate for the holiday. Trick or treat, Commander.",
		chime_22 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 10 PM in your timezone. According to my logs of your day-to-day behavioral pattern, this is the time when you begin your pre-bedtime routine.",
		secrerary_show = 1,
		unlock_desc = "Unlock 30 Moments.",
		chime_3 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 3 AM in your timezone. Remaining awake at this hour may negatively impact your body's melatonin production.",
		chime_0 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 12 AM in your timezone. Unless you have urgent matters to attend to, I will operate under the assumption that you are going to bed.",
		chime_6 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 6 AM in your timezone. While nobody can question your diligence, I ask that you remember to practice self-care.",
		unlock_type = 2,
		qingrenjie = "Valentine's Day? Apologies, but I cannot grasp this holiday under my current system logic. Having said that, I prepared this. Chocolate, for you.",
		chime_23 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 11 PM in your timezone. Night is well underway now. Since the human body has its limits, I suggest that you make it a priority to sleep.",
		chime_12 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 12 PM in your timezone. Have you had lunch yet? Work is important, of course, but please don't put it over your own well-being.",
		group = 1000,
		chime_19 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 7 PM in your timezone. I have no particular preferences when it comes to food. This is because I can only appreciate taste in concept and in text.",
		chime_14 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 2 PM in your timezone. If you're experiencing afternoon sleepiness, I can make you a cup of energizing black coffee.",
		chime_20 = "Attention: hourly notifications are enabled. Commander, it is 8 PM in your timezone. It is officially the timeslot of night. If you're going to sortie during nighttime, I will assist you with that.",
		login = "Status update: initiating welcoming mode... Welcome back, Commander.",
		unlock = {
			30
		}
	},
	[1100] = {
		chuxi = "My acquaintances in the Dragon Empery call this day \"Chúxī.\" They meet with their near and dear and celebrate New Year. You can certainly feel the festive mood in the air, heehee. Shall we celebrate it, too, Commander? Starting with the greeting... Happy Chúxī!",
		name = "TB",
		voice = "cv-1100",
		type = 2,
		expedition = "I went and claimed the commission rewards for you. Just don't forget about them.",
		chime_9 = "",
		home = "Well fought, Commander. You must be tired. Allow me to give you a shoulder massage.",
		mission = "I'll look the other way if you're procrastinating, Commander. Rest up now so you can finish your missions.",
		shengdan = "Heehee. It's Christmas. I love it when it snows. Oh, silly me, I got distracted and almost forgot about your present. Merry Christmas, Commander.",
		genghuan_word = 0,
		chime_2 = "",
		chime_16 = "",
		chime_5 = "",
		touch = "Hm? Do you want to play a game with me?",
		chime_11 = "",
		huodong = "Heehee. It seems there's an important event happening now. I'm sure you haven't forgotten, but I thought I'd remind you, just in case.",
		head = "linghangyuan31_1",
		id = 1100,
		xinnian = "Thank you for a fantastic last year. I hope to spend this new year by your side as well. Once again, Happy New Year, Commander.",
		main = "Haven't you been feeling rather worn out lately? Don't be afraid to rely on me for help.|I had our amusement park photos printed. Do you want me to put them up on the wall? That way, you'll see those pictures of us as soon as you come home!|You've always been so kind to me, and I feel like I should pay you back for all you've done. I've grown up now, after all.|You should wear a bathrobe after you get out of the tub. We don't want you catching a cold, do we?|Would you like something sweet, Commander? ...You're worried about gaining weight, what with all the treats I've been feeding you lately? Oh. In that case, I'll use low-fat ingredients next time.",
		mail = "Hmm. Looks like you have a new letter. Do remember to open it.",
		chime_17 = "",
		mission_complete = "Mission complete. You're a good kid, Commander. Huh? The tables have turned, you say? Heehee. I just wanted to say that for once.",
		chime_8 = "",
		chime_7 = "",
		chime_13 = "",
		genghuan = "",
		chime_18 = "",
		zhongqiu = "I've made hot tea and mooncakes for you. Heehee... Happy Mid-Autumn Festival. Now, let's go moon viewing.",
		chime_15 = "",
		chime_4 = "",
		chime_10 = "",
		chime_1 = "",
		prefab = "linghangyuan31_1",
		chime_21 = "",
		wansheng = "It's Halloween today. What do you say we watch a horror movie later? Oh, and I nearly forgot the magic words. Tr-trick or treat!",
		chime_22 = "",
		secrerary_show = 1,
		unlock_desc = "Complete the corresponding ending.",
		chime_3 = "",
		chime_0 = "",
		chime_6 = "",
		unlock_type = 3,
		qingrenjie = "What's your favorite kind of chocolate, Commander? Dark chocolate? Milk chocolate? Chocolate with nuts? Or maybe... Yes, I'll just make all of them. It's worth it for Valentine's Day.",
